Interface HdfsProxy

All Superinterfaces:
Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface HdfsProxy extends Remote
RMI interface for the HdfsProxy. See *kivakit-filesystems-hdfs-proxy* and *kivakit-filesystems-hdfs* for a detailed discussion.
